Package de.yamass.redg.runtime.defaultvalues.pluggable

Class PluggableDefaultValueStrategy

java.lang.Object
de.yamass.redg.runtime.defaultvalues.pluggable.PluggableDefaultValueStrategy
All Implemented Interfaces:
DefaultValueStrategy
public class PluggableDefaultValueStrategy extends Object implements DefaultValueStrategy
A DefaultValueStrategy that implements a simple plugin system. Add your PluggableDefaultValueProviders to it in the order they should be used.

Note: if your provider returns true for PluggableDefaultValueProvider.willProvide(ColumnModel), its value will be queried, even if it might not be used. A provider providing a not-null value will always be preferred.
